The paper focuses on improving the usability of fallback authentication, which is a human-computer interaction (HCI) issue, making cs.HC the most likely category. The paper also deals with security questions, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY). The use of serious games and game-based learning approaches also falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.SI). Finally, the paper mentions the use of pictures and cues, which is a topic related to computer graphics (cs.GR).
